  {
    "title": "The 5-minute morning routine",
    "date": "2026-01-11",
    "slug": "morning-routine",
    "category": "life",
    "tags": [],
    "content": "<p>A simple morning routine that sets the tone for the entire day.</p>\n<h2>The Routine</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Hydrate</strong> - Glass of water before anything else</li>\n<li><strong>Move</strong> - 2 minutes of stretching</li>\n<li><strong>Breathe</strong> - 10 deep breaths, focusing on exhale</li>\n<li><strong>Intention</strong> - One sentence: &quot;Today I will...&quot;</li>\n<li><strong>Start</strong> - Begin the most important task immediately</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Why It Works</h2>\n<p>The key insight: <strong>momentum compounds</strong>. Starting small removes friction. The hardest part is getting out of bed; everything after that is easier.</p>\n<h2>Tracking</h2>\n<p>I use a simple text file:</p>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"code-block-header\">\n          <span class=\"code-block-lang\"></span>\n          <button class=\"code-copy-btn\" aria-label=\"Copy code\">\n            <svg class=\"copy-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1\"></path></svg>\n            <svg class=\"check-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg>\n          </button>\n        </div>\n        <pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark\" style=\"--shiki-light:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#e1e4e8;--shiki-light-bg:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#24292e\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span>2026-01-11: intention=\"finish TIL site\" / completed=yes</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>2026-01-10: intention=\"review PRs\" / completed=partial</span></span></code></pre>\n      </div><p>No apps, no complexity. Just words.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>&quot;How you do anything is how you do everything.&quot;</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The morning sets the pattern.</p>\n",
    "navigation": {
